snippet.title: Kamaeru: A Frog Refuge - Release Date Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Kamaeru: A Frog Refuge is launching on June 8th, 2024! Coming to PC, Nintendo Switch, and Xbox Series X|S.

Collect, feed, and breed over 500 froggy friends as you work to restore biodiversity to the wetlands in this cozy farming sim from Humble Reeds. Hop right to it! 🐸

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1978150/Kamaeru_A_Frog_Refuge/
Pre-order on Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/kamaeru-a-frog-refuge-switch/
Follow Kamaeru on Twitter: https://x.com/Kamaeru_game
